#

Borshch with Pork

120 min
$12.99
250 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 6

Dietary Tags:

gluten-freehigh-protein

Cuisine:

Eastern European

Course:

Main Dish

Tags:

soupheartycomfort food

Description

A hearty and vibrant beet soup with tender pork, perfect for a comforting meal.

Ingredients

  • pork shoulder: 1 lb
  • beets: 3 medium
  • cabbage: 1/2 head
  • potatoes: 2 medium
  • carrots: 2 medium
  • onion: 1 large
  • tomato paste: 2 tbsp
  • garlic: 3 cloves
  • vegetable broth: 6 cups
  • sour cream: for serving
  • fresh dill: for garnish
